    "\"Transport\" is how the lookup travels. IP is unencrypted; DoH, DoT, and DoQ scramble it so others on your network can't see the sites you visit.": {
      "comment": "DNS Transport section footer explaining what the transport options mean.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "„Transport“ ist, wie die Abfrage reist. IP ist unverschlüsselt; DoH, DoT und DoQ verschlüsseln sie, damit andere im Netzwerk deine besuchten Seiten nicht sehen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Transport\" is how the lookup travels. IP is unencrypted; DoH, DoT, and DoQ scramble it so others on your network can't see the sites you visit."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Transport» es cómo viaja la consulta. IP va sin cifrar; DoH, DoT y DoQ la cifran para que otros en tu red no puedan ver los sitios que visitas."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le « Transport » est la façon dont la requête circule. IP n'est pas chiffré ; DoH, DoT et DoQ la brouillent pour que personne sur votre réseau ne voie les sites que vous visitez."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "«Transport» è come viaggia la richiesta. IP non è cifrato; DoH, DoT e DoQ la cifrano così che altri sulla tua rete non vedano i siti che visiti."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」は問い合わせの送られ方です。IP は暗号化なし。DoH・DoT・DoQ は暗号化するので、同じネットワークの人に訪問先を見られません。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」는 조회가 오가는 방식이에요. IP는 암호화되지 않아요. DoH, DoT, DoQ는 조회를 암호화해서 같은 네트워크의 다른 사람이 방문 사이트를 못 보게 해요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Transport\" é como a consulta viaja. O IP fica sem criptografia; DoH, DoT e DoQ a embaralham para que outros na sua rede não vejam os sites que você visita."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“Transport”指查询的传送方式。IP 不加密;DoH、DoT 和 DoQ 会加密,让同网络的人看不到你访问了哪些网站。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「Transport」是查詢傳送的方式。IP 未加密；DoH、DoT、DoQ 會加密，讓同網路的人看不到你造訪的網站。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
