    "A site you allow here always gets through, even if a blocklist would block it. Only add sites you fully trust.": {
      "comment": "Caution under the allowed-exceptions list. 'allow'/'blocklist' should match the catalog's Allowed Exceptions / blocklist renderings. Plain, reassuring tone.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Website, die du hier erlaubst, kommt immer durch, auch wenn eine Blockliste sie blockieren würde. Füge nur Websites hinzu, denen du voll vertraust."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A site you allow here always gets through, even if a blocklist would block it. Only add sites you fully trust."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un sitio que permitas aquí siempre pasa, aunque una lista de bloqueo lo bloquearía. Añade solo sitios en los que confíes plenamente."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un site que vous autorisez ici passe toujours, même si une liste de blocage le bloquerait. N'ajoutez que des sites en lesquels vous avez pleine confiance."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un sito che consenti qui passa sempre, anche se una lista di blocco lo bloccherebbe. Aggiungi solo siti di cui ti fidi pienamente."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ここで許可したサイトは、ブロックリストがブロックする場合でも常に通過します。完全に信頼できるサイトだけを追加してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "여기서 허용한 사이트는 차단 목록이 막더라도 항상 통과해요. 완전히 믿을 수 있는 사이트만 추가하세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Um site que você libera aqui sempre passa, mesmo que uma lista de bloqueio fosse bloqueá-lo. Adicione apenas sites em que você confia totalmente."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在这里允许的网站一律会通过,即使拦截列表会拦截它。请只添加你完全信任的网站。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在這裡允許的網站一律會通過,即使封鎖清單會封鎖它。請只新增你完全信任的網站。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "About 4 KB for current settings. Full blocklists are referenced by their ID in our catalog. All your settings are fully encrypted so even Lava can't see.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aktuelle Einstellungen brauchen etwa 4 KB. Vollständige Blocklisten werden über ihre ID in unserem Katalog referenziert. Alle Einstellungen sind vollständig verschlüsselt, sodass selbst Lava sie nicht sehen kann."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "About 4 KB for current settings. Full blocklists are referenced by their ID in our catalog. All your settings are fully encrypted, so even Lava can't see them."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Environ 4 Ko pour les réglages actuels. Les listes complètes sont référencées par leur ID dans notre catalogue. Tous vos réglages sont entièrement chiffrés, même Lava ne peut pas les lire."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "現在の設定は約 4 KB です。完全なブロックリストはカタログ内の ID で参照されます。すべての設定は完全に暗号化されるため Lava にも見えません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前设置约 4 KB。完整拦截列表会以目录中的 ID 引用。你的所有设置都会完全加密，Lava Security 也看不到。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "目前設定約 4 KB。完整封鎖清單會以我們目錄中的 ID 參照。你的所有設定都會完整加密，Lava Security 也看不到。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unos 4 KB para los ajustes actuales. Las listas de bloqueo completas se identifican por su ID en nuestro catálogo. Todos tus ajustes están totalmente cifrados, así que ni siquiera Lava puede verlos."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "현재 설정 기준 약 4KB예요. 전체 차단 목록은 카탈로그의 ID로 참조돼요. 모든 설정은 완전히 암호화되어 Lava도 볼 수 없어요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cerca de 4 KB para as configurações atuais. As listas de bloqueio completas são referenciadas pelo ID delas em nosso catálogo. Todas as suas configurações são totalmente criptografadas, então nem a Lava consegue ver."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Circa 4 KB per le impostazioni attuali. Le liste di blocco complete sono indicate dal loro ID nel nostro catalogo. Tutte le tue impostazioni sono completamente cifrate, così nemmeno Lava può vederle."
          }
        }
      }
    },
