    "Domain history and network activity are kept for 7 days; counts and Lava Guard progress last longer. Keep or clear each below.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Domain-Verlauf und Netzwerkaktivität bleiben 7 Tage; Zähler und Lava Guard-Fortschritt länger. Unten kannst du jedes behalten oder löschen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Domain history and network activity are kept for 7 days; counts and Lava Guard progress last longer. Keep or clear each below."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'historique des domaines et l'activité réseau sont gardés 7 jours ; les compteurs et la progression Lava Guard plus longtemps. Conservez ou effacez chacun ci-dessous."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ドメイン履歴とネットワークアクティビティは7日間保存。カウントと Lava Guard の進捗はもっと長く残ります。下で個別に保持・消去できます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "域名历史和网络活动保留 7 天,计数和 Lava Guard 进度保留更久。可在下方分别保留或清除。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "網域記錄和網路活動保留 7 天；計數和 Lava Guard 進度則更久。下方可分別保留或清除。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El historial de dominios y la actividad de red se guardan 7 días; los recuentos y el progreso de Lava Guard, más tiempo. Conserva o borra cada uno abajo."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "도메인 기록과 네트워크 활동은 7일간 보관돼요. 횟수와 Lava Guard 진행 상황은 더 오래 가요. 아래에서 각각 두거나 지우세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O histórico de domínios e a atividade de rede ficam por 7 dias; as contagens e o progresso do Lava Guard duram mais. Mantenha ou limpe cada um abaixo."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cronologia dei domini e attività di rete restano 7 giorni; conteggi e progressi di Lava Guard durano di più. Qui sotto conserva o cancella ciascuno."
          }
        }
      }
    },
