    "Local counts of how Lava handles your traffic. Nothing here shows the sites you visited, so look around freely.": {
      "comment": "Nerd Stats intro panel reassuring the counters reveal no browsing history.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lokale Zähler dazu, wie Lava deinen Verkehr verarbeitet. Nichts hier zeigt deine besuchten Seiten – schau dich ruhig um."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Local counts of how Lava handles your traffic. Nothing here shows the sites you visited, so look around freely."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Recuentos locales de cómo gestiona Lava tu tráfico. Aquí no se ven los sitios que visitaste, así que mira con tranquilidad."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Comptages locaux de la façon dont Lava gère votre trafic. Rien ici ne montre les sites visités, explorez librement."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Conteggi locali di come Lava gestisce il tuo traffico. Qui non c'è nulla sui siti che hai visitato, quindi guarda pure liberamente."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava が通信をどう扱ったかのローカルな集計です。訪れたサイトは表示されないので、安心して見て回れます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava가 트래픽을 어떻게 처리했는지 보여 주는 로컬 집계예요. 방문한 사이트는 여기 안 나오니 편하게 둘러보세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Totais locais de como a Lava lida com o seu tráfego. Nada aqui mostra os sites que você visitou, então pode olhar à vontade."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava 处理你流量方式的本地计数。这里不会显示你访问过的网站,可以放心查看。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava 處理你流量方式的本機計數。這裡不會顯示你造訪過的網站，放心看吧。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Local counts of how Lava reaches the internet — no website names. They track when lookups worked, failed, retried, or briefly fell back to your phone's settings.": {
      "comment": "Nerd Stats: footer under the Tunnel Health section. Plain-language, scannable summary of what the diagnostic counters mean; reassures that no website names are stored.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lokale Zähler dazu, wie Lava ins Internet kommt – keine Website-Namen. Sie zeigen, wann Abfragen klappten, fehlschlugen, wiederholt wurden oder kurz auf die Einstellungen deines Telefons zurückgingen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Local counts of how Lava reaches the internet — no website names. They track when lookups worked, failed, retried, or briefly fell back to your phone's settings."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Recuentos locales de cómo se conecta Lava a internet, sin nombres de sitios. Registran cuándo las búsquedas funcionaron, fallaron, se reintentaron o pasaron un momento a los ajustes de tu teléfono."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Comptages locaux de la façon dont Lava accède à internet — aucun nom de site. Ils suivent les recherches réussies, échouées, réessayées ou brièvement basculées vers les réglages de votre téléphone."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Conteggi locali di come Lava raggiunge internet — nessun nome di sito. Indicano quando le ricerche sono riuscite, fallite, ripetute o tornate per un attimo alle impostazioni del telefono."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava がインターネットにどうつながったかのローカル集計で、サイト名は含みません。照会の成功・失敗・再試行や、一時的に端末の設定に戻った回数を示します。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava가 인터넷에 어떻게 연결하는지 보여 주는 로컬 집계예요. 사이트 이름은 없어요. 조회가 성공·실패·재시도되거나 휴대폰 설정으로 잠깐 되돌아간 횟수를 세요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Totais locais de como a Lava acessa a internet — sem nomes de sites. Mostram quando as buscas funcionaram, falharam, foram repetidas ou recorreram um instante aos ajustes do seu telefone."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava 连接互联网方式的本地计数,不含网站名。记录查询成功、失败、重试,或短暂切回手机设置的次数。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lava 如何連上網路的本機計數 — 不含網站名稱。記錄查詢成功、失敗、重試，或短暫切回手機設定的次數。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
