    "The server only stores encrypted backup data. The key stays with you.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Server speichert nur verschlüsselte Backup-Daten. Der Schlüssel bleibt bei dir."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The server only stores encrypted backup data. The key stays with you."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le serveur ne stocke que des données de sauvegarde chiffrées. La clé reste avec vous."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サーバーに保存されるのは暗号化済みのバックアップデータだけです。鍵はあなたの手元に残ります。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "服务器只保存加密的备份数据。密钥由你保管。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "伺服器只儲存加密的備份資料。金鑰由你保管。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El servidor solo guarda los datos de la copia de seguridad cifrados. La clave se queda contigo."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "서버에는 암호화된 백업 데이터만 저장돼요. 키는 사용자에게만 있어요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O servidor só guarda os dados de backup criptografados. A chave fica com você."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il server conserva solo dati di backup cifrati. La chiave resta a te."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These switches turn on after you set a passcode or Face ID above. Each one decides which screen asks before it lets you in.": {
      "comment": "Security section footer explaining the per-screen lock toggles.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Diese Schalter werden aktiv, sobald du oben einen Code oder Face ID eingerichtet hast. Jeder bestimmt, welcher Bildschirm fragt, bevor er dich hineinlässt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "These switches turn on after you set a passcode or Face ID above. Each one decides which screen asks before it lets you in."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Estos interruptores se activan después de que configures un código o Face ID más arriba. Cada uno decide qué pantalla te pide la verificación antes de dejarte entrar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ces interrupteurs s'activent après avoir défini un code ou Face ID ci-dessus. Chacun décide quel écran demande une vérification avant de vous laisser entrer."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questi interruttori si attivano dopo che imposti un codice o Face ID qui sopra. Ognuno decide quale schermata chiede la verifica prima di farti entrare."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これらのスイッチは、上でパスコードか Face ID を設定すると有効になります。それぞれ、どの画面が入る前に確認を求めるかを決めます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 스위치들은 위에서 암호나 Face ID를 설정한 뒤에 켜져요. 각 스위치는 어떤 화면이 들어가기 전에 확인을 요청할지 정해요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Estes botões são ativados depois que você define um código ou o Face ID acima. Cada um decide qual tela pede a verificação antes de deixar você entrar."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在上方设置密码或 Face ID 后,这些开关才会启用。每一个都决定哪个屏幕在让你进入前会先要求验证。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在上方設定密碼或 Face ID 後,這些開關才會啟用。每一個都決定哪個畫面在讓你進入前會先要求驗證。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This deletes the signed-in Lava account and its encrypted backup from Lava's servers. Local protection settings stay on this device.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep placeholders and product names intact.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dies löscht das angemeldete Lava-Konto und sein verschlüsseltes Backup von Lavas Servern. Lokale Schutzeinstellungen bleiben auf diesem Gerät."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This deletes the signed-in Lava account and its encrypted backup from Lava's servers. Local protection settings stay on this device."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cela supprime le compte Lava connecté et sa sauvegarde chiffrée des serveurs Lava. Les réglages de protection locale restent sur cet appareil."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サインイン中の Lava アカウントと暗号化バックアップを Lava のサーバーから削除します。ローカル保護の設定はこのデバイスに残ります。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会从 Lava Security 服务器删除已登录的 Lava Security 账户及其加密备份。本地防护设置会留在这台设备上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會從 Lava Security 伺服器刪除已登入的 Lava Security 帳號及其加密備份。本機防護設定會留在這台裝置上。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto elimina la cuenta de Lava con la que has iniciado sesión y su copia de seguridad cifrada de los servidores de Lava. Los ajustes de protección local permanecen en este dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "로그인된 Lava 계정과 그 암호화 백업을 Lava 서버에서 삭제해요. 로컬 보호 설정은 이 기기에 그대로 남아요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Isso exclui a conta Lava conectada e o backup criptografado dela dos servidores da Lava. As configurações de proteção local ficam neste aparelho."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questo elimina dai server di Lava l'account Lava con cui hai eseguito l'accesso e il suo backup cifrato. Le impostazioni di protezione locale restano su questo dispositivo."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is separate from your account login and is required to decrypt your backup.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Das ist getrennt von deiner Kontoanmeldung und zum Entschlüsseln deines Backups nötig."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This is separate from your account login and is required to decrypt your backup."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "C’est séparé de la connexion au compte et sert à déchiffrer la sauvegarde."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これはアカウントログインとは別で、バックアップの復号に必要です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这与账户登录不同，是解密备份所必需的。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這與你的帳號登入不同，解密備份時必須使用。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto es independiente del inicio de sesión de tu cuenta y es necesario para descifrar tu copia de seguridad."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이는 계정 로그인과 별개이며, 백업을 복호화하는 데 필요해요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Isso é separado do login da sua conta e é necessário para descriptografar o seu backup."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È separata dall'accesso al tuo account ed è necessaria per decifrare il tuo backup."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This recovery code unlocks the backup if the password is lost. Setup will continue after it has been copied.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dieser Wiederherstellungscode entsperrt das Backup, falls das Passwort verloren geht. Nach dem Kopieren geht die Einrichtung weiter."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This recovery code unlocks the backup if the password is lost. Setup will continue after it has been copied."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ce code de récupération déverrouille la sauvegarde si le mot de passe est perdu. La configuration continue après la copie."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "パスワードをなくした場合、このリカバリーコードでバックアップを開けます。コピー後に設定を続行します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果密码丢失，此恢复码可解锁备份。复制后设置才会继续。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如果密碼遺失，這組復原碼可解鎖備份。複製後設定才會繼續。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Este código de recuperación desbloquea la copia de seguridad si pierdes la contraseña. La configuración continuará una vez que lo hayas copiado."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 복구 코드는 비밀번호를 잃어버렸을 때 백업을 풀어줘요. 복사한 뒤에 설정이 이어져요."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Este código de recuperação desbloqueia o backup se a senha for perdida. A configuração continua depois que ele for copiado."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Questo codice di recupero sblocca il backup se perdi la password. La configurazione proseguirà dopo che lo avrai copiato."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This removes saved Domain Logs from this phone. Filtering counts and network activity are unchanged.": {
      "comment": "Release app UI string. Keep product/legal terms from the glossary unchanged and review before final release.",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dies entfernt gespeicherte Domain-Protokolle von diesem Smartphone. Filterzähler und Netzwerkaktivität bleiben unverändert."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This removes saved Domain Logs from this phone. Filtering counts and network activity are unchanged."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cela supprime les journaux de domaines enregistrés sur ce téléphone. Les compteurs de filtrage et l’activité réseau ne changent pas."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このスマートフォンに保存されたドメインログを削除します。フィルタリング数とネットワークアクティビティは変わりません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会移除这台手机上保存的域名日志。过滤计数和网络活动不会改变。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會移除此手機上儲存的網域日誌。篩選計數和網路活動不會改變。"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Esto elimina los registros de dominios guardados en este teléfono. Los recuentos de filtrado y la actividad de red no cambian."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 휴대폰에 저장된 도메인 로그를 삭제해요. 필터링 횟수와 네트워크 활동은 그대로예요."
